  "keyFeatures": [
    "Smart play with auto-detection of artist, album, or track",
    "Spotify Web API search (no Premium required)",
    "AppleScript-based playback control (no focus stealing)",
    "Concurrent multi-type search using tokio",
    "Custom aliases for frequent searches",
    "Full playback controls: pause, resume, next, prev, volume, shuffle, repeat",
    "Token caching with 1-hour TTL",
    "No subcommand needed — `spot <query>` just works"
